    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Sept 16 article: Ford Motor Co sought to buy Kia Motors in 1998, not 1988</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Because of an editing error, an article in Business Day on Saturday about interest shown by foreign automakers in South Korea's automotive industry misstated the year the Ford Motor Company sought to buy Kia Motors. It was 1998, not 1988. Also because of an editing error, the article misstated the site of an interview with Peter A. Underwood, a consultant who advises foreign companies about doing business in South Korea. He was reached in Seoul by telephone from Tokyo, not interviewed in Seoul.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
